            . I am ten years old. On the 21st of October I was standing by my father's workshop in <placeName id="t18201028-128-crimeloc699">Shoreditch</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18201028-128-crimeloc699" type="placeName" value="Shoreditch"></interp>
